{"tid":933750,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人想象唔到有人愛自己？","createTime":"2018-12-08T17:26:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-09T20:23:54.000Z","uid":207336,"like":49,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"85c1ab2c08755c7e55c1268a4ccf3fdcafaa416e","tid":933750,"uid":207336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T17:26:54.000Z","msg":"睇到啲人愛得咁癡纏，真係好難想象主角係自己會點，覺得唔會有人會愛自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d8a12c3a27aa77851481a395098d3593c80cccd","tid":933750,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T17:39:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcad123844e7cfb35801348f533220c44a68f0eb","tid":933750,"uid":112065,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T17:48:03.000Z","msg":"我覺架巴打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明明每個人都係一個獨立個體，點會有一個人會為另一個人咁死心塌地對佢好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能自己防禦心太強掛，我諗我唔會有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8bc10bc39a028165cad0a6e16d724f93ee2790e","tid":933750,"uid":52448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T17:52:35.000Z","msg":"巴打覺得自己因為咩唔會有人愛?"},{"pid":"ef34e2c7f61fc5fcdd45182ccd669989d0e4b20d","tid":933750,"uid":2816,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T18:07:52.000Z","msg":"太長時間未愛過,又未被愛過<br />\n就來連幸福也害怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ab3bf66433dfdff91fbd2c21f10cb0061d2691b","tid":933750,"uid":155062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T18:53:41.000Z","msg":"係 自己條件太差 唔會有人肯好好認識我 愛我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bf84a017a07137b733f7d54b979a397c4666079","tid":933750,"uid":198607,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T19:13:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 每次都係自己單方面 想像唔到有人會好似我stalk佢咁stalk我"},{"pid":"45877109f9d7ed5a4bfcfb6d2e3407151557b638","tid":933750,"uid":37713,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T20:17:53.000Z","msg":"自己咁差真係好難想像有人會真心咁愛上自己<br />\n就算真係有條友同我表白都覺得佢係咪夾埋班fd玩緊我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又或者形住形住佢再深入少少認識我就會走夾唔頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33463312efe5809c4c9399dd676cf7e4cd14c84a","tid":933750,"uid":196590,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T08:03:31.000Z","msg":"次次都同人曖昧完比對方拋低 成日諗自己係咪唔值得被人愛"},{"pid":"ee8cd11d7510dc98aff027262ba703109cc930ba","tid":933750,"uid":205856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T08:04:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c06312be1d68e3bf3cd0b98ef9e33d869aa191b2","tid":933750,"uid":143427,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T09:11:17.000Z","msg":"由細到大都未俾人寵過愛過，好多時我都覺得連自己老豆老母都未試過對我咁好，你會？<br />\n<br />\n親人都冇攬過我更加冇講過愛我，所以我都好難想像外人會咁做，我甚至唔渴望唔想人地對我太好因為我都唔知要俾咩反應好，我真心想象唔到有人愛自己，就算有我都會唔信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce57293bd9de066fb57cb7e78be396e116550918","tid":933750,"uid":225102,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T11:40:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb40ddbc24be6f9d7f2a8185742a1c8f0a034b2a","tid":933750,"uid":91096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c06312be1d68e3bf3cd0b98ef9e33d869aa191b2","tid":933750,"uid":143427,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T09:11:17.000Z","msg":"由細到大都未俾人寵過愛過，好多時我都覺得連自己老豆老母都未試過對我咁好，你會？<br />\n<br />\n親人都冇攬過我更加冇講過愛我，所以我都好難想像外人會咁做，我甚至唔渴望唔想人地對我太好因為我都唔知要俾咩反應好，我真心想象唔到有人愛自己，就算有我都會唔信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" clas